        public int CON_ConnectDevices(java.lang.String printName,
                     java.lang.String port,
                     int timeout)
        Connect to printer
        参数:
        printName - print device name
        port - port name
        Bluetooth Bluetooth MAC address or name RG-MTP58B/02:5B:B3:A3:03:55
        WIFI IP address and port combination 192.168.1.156:9100
        USB Fixed name USB
        Serial Serial name , baudrate,permission（1：yes（default）；other no）and flow control（0：NONE；1：SOFT；2：HARDWARE（default）） /dev/ttyS0:9600:1:1
        timeout - connect time out
        返回:
        0 Open port failure Nonzero Object connection after the success of the value, use the return value to represent the interface of related objects will in the future to print in the API call

      • CON_PageStart

        public int CON_PageStart(int objCode,
                boolean graphicMode,
                int width,
                int height)
        Enter print mode, after a successful connection call this function to open the print function, Called to "DRAW _" prefix to print the drawing function, the other to the corresponding language text printing Finally, call # CON_PageEnd (int, TransferMode) CON_PageEnd () End page of text or graphics data cache; to send data cache
        参数:
        objCode - The one opened object target
        graphicMode - Whether to use the graphics mode to print, false uses built-in Font printer to print the contents of the content, then be called text print function; true makes use of graphics to print, then print contents can call text print function (label machine) or graphic print function
        width - The maximum width of text mode graphics mode or label printing machine, 384 (58mm wide) or 576 (80mm wide)
        height - Text mode graphics mode or label machine under the maximum printing height, size is no limit, but when entering the graphics mode, the higher the height represents the cache more data, when the height of more than 1500 can cause abnormal program cache
        返回:
        true presents send it out success, or it is failure
